00:01:18,413 --> 00:01:21,514
[SPEAKER_16]: Sincerely yours, Nicole Morrell, Council President.

30
00:01:22,394 --> 00:01:25,935
[SPEAKER_16]: So this meeting has been called to discuss the draft tree ordinance.

31
00:01:26,816 --> 00:01:32,197
[SPEAKER_16]: We met in February and again in June regarding this draft ordinance.

32
