00:04:58,778 --> 00:05:14,092
[SPEAKER_08]: Um, so I do have some, some motions for later, um, in the discussion, but I think there are some policy decisions we could make to tonight to decide, um, whether we want to strike some things or move them things out into separate ordinances, um, so that we could get a more clear draft.

