571
00:56:15,024 --> 00:56:15,465
[SPEAKER_01]: We're trying.

572
00:56:15,805 --> 00:56:16,225
[SPEAKER_01]: It's hard.

573
00:56:18,347 --> 00:56:20,008
[SPEAKER_01]: You can ask your director and your

574
00:56:22,002 --> 00:56:26,648
