579
00:56:44,871 --> 00:56:50,974
[SPEAKER_08]: So if I could make just one motion while I'm still here, I would just, thank you.

580
00:56:51,054 --> 00:57:06,222
[SPEAKER_08]: I would just motion that we request that planning development and sustainability, DPW and finance meet to provide comments on both the draft of the tree ordinance, as well as the proposed draft around the moratorium in advance of a future meeting.

581
00:57:08,848 --> 00:57:19,451
[SPEAKER_16]: All right, so the motion is that PDS, DPW, and the finance department meet to discuss and make comments on the draft prior to a future meeting.

582
00:57:20,431 --> 00:57:22,851
[SPEAKER_08]: Correct, and including the moratorium draft as well.

583
00:57:24,592 --> 00:57:27,693
[SPEAKER_16]: On the draft, on draft and moratorium.

584
00:57:27,793 --> 00:57:37,635
[SPEAKER_08]: And I do know there were, we do have comments from DPW already, if it's beneficial to just have that, you know, comments where different departments can talk to each other and understand how this might interplay.

