00:58:10,996 --> 00:58:12,497
[SPEAKER_08]: President Morrell.

593
00:58:12,537 --> 00:58:14,658
[SPEAKER_08]: I have to, let me pull it up.

594
00:58:14,958 --> 00:58:19,760
[SPEAKER_08]: But I think, I mean, the comments on the moratorium could be as simply as like, I don't think this is feasible.

595
00:58:19,840 --> 00:58:27,784
