[SPEAKER_16]: We can continue discussion after those motions, but on the motion to request that planning development, sustainability, DPW and finance meet to discuss and make comments on the draft, as well as a draft moratorium ordinance, seconded by councilor saying, Mr. Clerk, please call the roll.

